  Search by species, genus or family name, or any words describing the plant:
  <input type="search" data-action="filters#findResults" class="form-control block w-full px-3 py-1.5 text-base font-normal text-gray-700 bg-white bg-clip-padding  border border-solid border-gray-300 rounded transition  ease-in-out m-0 focus:text-gray-700 focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-600 focus:outline-none">
</div>

